::Zardus::

Zardus enters the bridge in time to hear Nemesis Enforcer ask for orders. The 
Alliance commander looks at him, glancing at the scanners.

"Panzertron contacted me a short while ago, something might be up," he says 
to his second-in-command, "We might go and meet with him later."
